pageContext.claim: “They went after Manafort -- using -- you know the big black book on Manafort? Turned out to be a fraud. They found that out recently. The black book where they said he got money, got cash, he got all -- turned out to be a fraud. Ukraine said that. All of these things that they did, they were set ups.”
pageContext.analysis: This is nonsense. Manafort pleaded guilty to several charges of fraud and witness tampering based on voluminous evidence of wrongdoing and financial transactions.
